data.description:
MOTIVATED SELLER!!!!  Welcome to your dream home in the highly sought-after Grain Valley School District! This stunning atrium split home offers an abundance of space, modern updates, and an exceptional backyard oasis, making it the perfect place for you and your family to call home. Spacious and comfortable, this home offers five bedrooms,(2 are non conforming) providing ample room for a growing family or accommodating guests. With four beautifully updated bathrooms, there's no more morning rush for the shower. This home boasts vaulted ceilings, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere for family gatherings or entertainment. Enjoy the freshness of newly updated walls, trim, and gleaming hardwood floors, which lend a touch of sophistication to the home. The heart of this home is the completely updated kitchen, where you'll find modern conveniences and plenty of space to prepare your favorite meals. Abundant of natural light: Vaulted ceilings and large windows throughout the home allow natural light to flood in, creating a bright and welcoming ambiance. Every corner of the home is illuminated with new, stylish fixtures that enhance the overall aesthetic. Brand new window coverings add privacy and style to every room. Backyard Paradise. Step outside to discover a wonderful backyard area, perfect for entertaining. The highlight is the new 12x24 ft pool, where you can relax and cool off on hot summer days. A spacious shed provides plenty of room for all your outdoor equipment and tools.
Nestled in the highly desirable Grain Valley School District, this home is conveniently located near excellent schools, parks, shopping, and dining options. You'll have everything you need right at your fingertips. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite property your forever home. Schedule a viewing today to see the comforts and all this home has to offer.
